	   <tr><td colspan=2>OMG. this stuff looks soooo awesome. I have had so many people tell me how cool it looks.  But you know what? For as hard as it is to make and as rare as it is...it sux ass.  Tunic 12ac...hmm banded tunic 14ac.  SO, not good for tanks. Great for casters, right? WRONG. the chest arms and legs I wore for the graphics were the exact ac as the crystalline robes, gatorscale sleeves and hand woven legs I had previous.  So, it's only good if it's enchanted or imbued right? WRONG!  Imbued can only be worn by followers of Innoruk, but they can easily get better. and the enchanted requires blue diamonds to make if you dont follow Innorukk. and the stats STILL BLOW.  I thought I was cool cause I'd only seen 2 other sets on the server, then I realized it's because the stuff sucks.  And I can't sell it now, so I guess I just let it rot in the bank and pull it out for weddings or something stupid like that. =/  Nice try verant, but this stuff is garbage.  <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
